text: Investigating the effect of Cryptomeria japonica D . Don essential oil on the LPS - treated RAW 264 . 7 cells , through enzyme immunoassay , some researchers reported the remarkable inhibition of IL - 1β , IL - 6 and TNF - α by that oil [ 115 ] . In this essential oil , kaurene , elemol , γ - eudesmol and sabinene prevailed .
